name: Antonov Airlines An-124-100M [UR-82007] Landing and Close Up Taxi at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Filming an Antonov An-124 on Delta 6 has been something I've wanted to do for the longest time, and here it finally is! Here we have UR-82007, one of the 7 An-124s in Antonov Airlines' fleet landing on runway 35R and taxiing ridiculously close up while vacating the runway at Calgary International Airport. ATC is included, hope you enjoy this evening arrival!

Thanks for watching!
